column2: Can talk others into doing things
Holds back from expressing my opinions
Enjoys being part of a group
Lets things proceed at their own pace
Is not easily bothered by things
Is calm, even in tense situations
Is afraid that I will do the wrong thing
Does not have a good imagination
Is not interested in abstract ideas
Believes in the importance of art
Prefers to stick with things that I know
Tends to vote for conservative political candidates
Often forgets to put things back in their proper place
Doesn’t see the consequences of things
